  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wireless/\" rel=\"tag\">无线应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/intel-smart-headset-offline-voice-recognition/\"><img alt=\"Intel Jarvis headset\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/cef6af414ce1d67a1d18322e44e217b3/ajs-ces2014_0303.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n各位还记得之前在 CES 2014 上赚得不少眼球的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/07/jarvis-is-intels-smart-earpiece/\">Jarvis</a> 智能蓝牙耳机吗？今天英特尔在接受 Quartz 采访时，透露了这款产品在离线状态下也能处理语音指令的消息。Jarvis 无需连线服务器便能听懂使用者的要求，这在没有网络的环境中非常实用，同时也让 Jarvis 在面对 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googlenow\">Google Now</a> 和 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/siri\">Siri</a> 这样的对手时有了更强的竞争力。值得一提的是，英特尔打算将相关技术授权给其它厂商，这样一来，就算不买 Jarvis 也有可能享受到同样的「福利」啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/28/intel-smart-headset-offline-voice-recognition/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://qz.com/170668/intels-voice-recognition-will-blow-siri-out-of-the-water-because-it-doesnt-use-the-cloud/#/\" target=\"_blank\">Quartz</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/intel-smart-headset-offline-voice-recognition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20817665/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/intel-smart-headset-offline-voice-recognition/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
